activities.name: Group_Chg_Accounts
activities.description: Makes default dynamic group for Accounts

source.query:
SELECT DISTINCT
'A' as object_type,
'D' as group_type,
'A' as function_enum            ,
S.id as organization_id,
'All accounts' as name                     ,
'All accounts' as description              ,
(select extract(epoch from now()) * 1000) as created_at,
CASE WHEN L.organization_id IS NULL THEN 'I' ELSE 'X' END AS CHG_FLG,
CURRENT_TIMeSTAMP AS LOAD_DT
from master.organization S
left join master.group L
ON S.ID = L.organization_id
where ('D' <> L.group_type OR
  'A'  <> L.function_enum OR
  'All accounts'  <> L.name  OR
  'All accounts' <> L.description OR
  L.organization_id IS NULL)
  
  UNION

SELECT DISTINCT
'V' as object_type,
'D' as group_type,
'A' as function_enum            ,
S.id as organization_id,
'Fleet' as name                     ,
'Fleet' as description              ,
(select extract(epoch from now()) * 1000) as created_at,
CASE WHEN L.organization_id IS NULL THEN 'I' ELSE 'X' END AS CHG_FLG,
CURRENT_TIMeSTAMP AS LOAD_DT
from master.organization S
left join master.group L
ON S.ID = L.organization_id
where ('D' <> L.group_type OR
  'A'  <> L.function_enum OR
  'Fleet'  <> L.name  OR
  'Fleet' <> L.description OR
  L.organization_id IS NULL);

SELECT 
E.object_type       ,
E.group_type                  ,
E.function_enum,
E.organization_id,
E.name,
E.description,
E.created_at
FROM staging.Group_CHG E
WHERE  E.CHG_FLG = 'I' 
AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM MASTER.GROUP L
             WHERE    L.organization_id = E.organization_id)
ORDER BY 
    	E.organization_id;

UPDATE MASTER.GROUP L 
SET	 
object_type	=	S.object_type  ,
group_type	=	S.group_type,  
function_enum	=	S.function_enum  ,
name	=	S.name  ,
description	=	S.description  
FROM    staging.GROUP_CHG S
WHERE L.organization_id = S.organization_id 
  AND  S.CHG_FLG     = 'X';

SELECT * FROM STAGING.GROUP_CHG;

activities.name: Organization_CHG
activities.description: Compares source and target and find the records for upsert

source.query:
SELECT 
	coalesce(L.ID,0) AS ID,
S.ORG_ID                        ,
S.TYPE                          ,
S.NAME                          ,
S.ADDRESS_TYPE                  ,
S.STREET                        ,
substring(S.STREET,'[0-9]+')  as STREET_NUMBER                  ,
S.POSTAL_CODE                   ,
S.CITY                          ,
CASE WHEN S.COUNTRY_CODE  IS NOT NULL THEN cnty.code ELSE NULL END AS country_code,
(select extract(epoch from cast(S.reference_date as timestamp)) * 1000) as REFERENCE_DATE,
S.PREFERENCE_ID                 ,
S.VEHICLE_DEFAULT_OPT_IN        ,
S.DRIVER_DEFAULT_OPT_IN         ,
S.STATE                         ,
	CASE WHEN L.ID IS NULL THEN 'I' ELSE 'X' END AS CHG_FLG,
	CURRENT_TIMeSTAMP AS LOAD_DT
	
FROM
       public.organization S
LEFT JOIN 
       master.organization L
ON S.ORG_ID = L.ORG_ID
LEFT join master.country cnty
on s.country_code = cnty.name
WHERE ( S.TYPE	<>	L.TYPE	OR
S.NAME	<>	L.NAME	OR
S.ADDRESS_TYPE	<>	L.ADDRESS_TYPE	OR
S.STREET	<>	L.STREET	OR
S.STREET_NUMBER	<>	L.STREET_NUMBER	OR
S.POSTAL_CODE	<>	L.POSTAL_CODE	OR
S.CITY	<>	L.CITY	OR
S.COUNTRY_CODE	<>	L.COUNTRY_CODE	OR
(select extract(epoch from cast(S.reference_date as timestamp)) * 1000)	<>	L.REFERENCE_DATE	OR
S.PREFERENCE_ID	<>	L.PREFERENCE_ID	OR
S.VEHICLE_DEFAULT_OPT_IN	<>	L.VEHICLE_DEFAULT_OPT_IN	OR
S.DRIVER_DEFAULT_OPT_IN	<>	L.DRIVER_DEFAULT_OPT_IN	OR
S.STATE	<>	L.STATE  OR
	    L.ID IS NULL);

UPDATE MASTER.ORGANIZATION L 
SET	 
TYPE	=	E.TYPE	,
NAME	=	E.NAME	,
ADDRESS_TYPE	=	E.ADDRESS_TYPE	,
STREET	=	E.STREET	,
STREET_NUMBER	=	E.STREET_NUMBER	,
POSTAL_CODE	=	E.POSTAL_CODE	,
CITY	=	E.CITY	,
COUNTRY_CODE	=	E.COUNTRY_CODE	,
REFERENCE_DATE	=	E.REFERENCE_DATE	,
PREFERENCE_ID	=	E.PREFERENCE_ID	,
VEHICLE_DEFAULT_OPT_IN	=	E.VEHICLE_DEFAULT_OPT_IN	,
DRIVER_DEFAULT_OPT_IN	=	E.DRIVER_DEFAULT_OPT_IN	,
STATE	=	E.STATE
FROM    staging.organization_chg E
WHERE L.org_id = E.org_id 
  AND  E.CHG_FLG     = 'X';
  
SELECT * FROM STAGING.ORGANIZATION_CHG WHERE CHG_FLG = 'X';

SELECT 
	E.ORG_ID                        ,
	E.NAME                          ,
	E.ADDRESS_TYPE                  ,
	CASE WHEN E.STREET  IS NOT NULL THEN E.STREET ELSE '' END AS STREET  ,
	CASE WHEN E.STREET_NUMBER  IS NOT NULL THEN E.STREET_NUMBER ELSE '' END AS STREET_NUMBER ,
	CASE WHEN E.POSTAL_CODE  IS NOT NULL THEN E.POSTAL_CODE ELSE '' END AS POSTAL_CODE                 ,
	CASE WHEN E.CITY IS NOT NULL THEN E.CITY ELSE '' END AS CITY                         ,
	CASE WHEN E.COUNTRY_CODE IS NOT NULL THEN E.COUNTRY_CODE ELSE '' END AS COUNTRY_CODE                 ,
	E.REFERENCE_DATE                ,
	E.VEHICLE_DEFAULT_OPT_IN        ,
	E.DRIVER_DEFAULT_OPT_IN         ,
	E.STATE                
	
FROM staging.Organization_CHG E
WHERE  E.CHG_FLG = 'I' 
AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM MASTER.ORGANIZATION L
             WHERE    L.ORG_ID = E.ORG_ID)
ORDER BY 
    	ORG_ID;

select distinct vh.id,prty.id as organization_id,vh.name as Name,vh.VIN,vh.plate_number as license_plate_number,
vh.connected_object_status as status,     
null as status_changed_date,
null as termination_date,
vh.vehicle_vid as vid,typ.type as type,
eq.supplier_serial_number as tcu_id,
eq.serial_number as tcu_serial_number,
vh.brand as tcu_brand,
'1.0' as tcu_version,
CASE WHEN eq.serial_number is not null then 'True' ELSE 'False' END is_tcu_register,
NULL as reference_date,
NULL as vehicle_property_id,
vh.creation_date as created_at,
vh.model_name as model_id,
1 as oem_id,
2 as oem_organisation_id,
'H' as opt_in,
vh.last_modification_date as modified_at,
'False' as is_ota,
null as modified_by,
REPLACE(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.fuelType'),'"','') as fuel_type
from cle_pc_cvp_fap.vehicle vh
left join daf.co_connected_object co
on co.internal_id = vh.vehicle_vid
left join daf.co_connected_object_type typ
on typ.id = co.connected_object_type
left join daf.co_third_party prty
on typ.third_party_id = prty.id
left join cle_pc_cvp_fap.equipment eq
on eq.vehicle_id = vh.id;

activities.name: Vehicle_CHG
activities.description: Compares source and target and find the records for upsert

source.query:
SELECT 
	coalesce(L.ID,0) AS ID,
ORG.ID  as ORGANIZATION_ID,
S.NAME,
S.VIN,
S.LICENSE_PLATE_NUMBER,
CASE WHEN  S.STATUS IN ('OPERATING','RESUMING','CREATED','READY','CONNECTED') THEN 'C'
     WHEN  S.STATUS = 'TERMINATING' THEN 'T'
     WHEN  S.STATUS = 'SUSPENDED' THEN 'O'
END AS STATUS,     
S.STATUS_CHANGED_DATE,
S.TERMINATION_DATE,
S.VID,
CASE WHEN S.TYPE = 'RIGID_HEAVY_TRUCK' THEN 'R'
     WHEN S.TYPE = 'ARTICULATED_TRUCK' THEN 'A'
	 WHEN S.TYPE = 'LCV' THEN 'L'
     WHEN S.TYPE = 'TRAILER' THEN 'T'	 
	 WHEN S.TYPE = 'VL'  THEN 'V'
	 WHEN S.TYPE = 'SEMITRAILER' THEN 'S'
	 WHEN S.TYPE = 'NONE' THEN 'N'
	 ELSE 'N' END AS TYPE,
S.TCU_ID,
S.TCU_SERIAL_NUMBER,
S.TCU_BRAND,
S.TCU_VERSION,
S.IS_TCU_REGISTER,
S.REFERENCE_DATE,
VP.ID AS VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ID,
(SELECT EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM CAST(S.CREATED_AT AS TIMESTAMP)) * 1000) AS  CREATED_AT, 
S.MODEL_ID,
CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(S.VIN,1,3) IS NOT NULL AND SUBSTRING(S.VIN,1,3) = TRIM(OM.VIN_PREFIX)
     THEN OM.ID
     ELSE (SELECT ID FROM MASTER.OEM WHERE TRIM(VIN_PREFIX) ISNULL)  END AS OEM_ID,
CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(S.VIN,1,3) IS NOT NULL AND SUBSTRING(S.VIN,1,3) = TRIM(OM.VIN_PREFIX)
     THEN OM.OEM_ORGANISATION_ID 
     ELSE (SELECT OEM_ORGANISATION_ID FROM MASTER.OEM WHERE TRIM(VIN_PREFIX) ISNULL)  END  AS OEM_ORGANISATION_ID, 
CASE WHEN S.STATUS = 'SUSPENDED' THEN 'U' ELSE 'H' END AS OPT_IN,
(SELECT EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM CAST(S.MODIFIED_AT AS TIMESTAMP)) * 1000) AS MODIFIED_AT,
S.IS_OTA,
S.MODIFIED_BY,
S.FUEL_TYPE,
	CASE WHEN L.ID IS NULL THEN 'I' ELSE 'X' END AS CHG_FLG,
	CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS LOAD_DT
	
FROM
       public.Vehicle S
LEFT JOIN PUBLIC.ORGANIZATION ORG_CT1
ON ORG_CT1.ID = S.ORGANIZATION_ID
LEFT JOIN MASTER.ORGANIZATION ORG
ON ORG.ORG_ID = ORG_CT1.ORG_ID
LEFT JOIN PUBLIC.VEHICLEPROPERTIES PVP
ON PVP.VEHICLE_VID = S.VID
LEFT JOIN MASTER.VEHICLEPROPERTIES VP
ON VP.CHASIS_ID = PVP.CHASIS_ID
LEFT JOIN MASTER.OEM OM
ON OM.VIN_PREFIX = SUBSTRING(S.VIN,1,3) AND OM.VIN_PREFIX IS NOT NULL	   
LEFT JOIN 
       master.Vehicle L
ON S.VID = L.VID  AND L.VIN = S.VIN
WHERE S.VIN IS NOT NULL AND ( ORG.ID <>	L.ORGANIZATION_ID	OR
S.name	<>	L.name	OR
S.license_plate_number	<>	L.license_plate_number	OR
CASE WHEN  S.STATUS IN ('OPERATING','RESUMING','CREATED','READY','CONNECTED') THEN 'C'
     WHEN  S.STATUS = 'TERMINATING' THEN 'T'
     WHEN  S.STATUS = 'SUSPENDED' THEN 'O'
END	<>	L.status	OR
S.status_changed_date	<>	L.status_changed_date	OR
S.termination_date	<>	L.termination_date	OR
CASE WHEN S.TYPE = 'RIGID_HEAVY_TRUCK' THEN 'R'
     WHEN S.TYPE = 'ARTICULATED_TRUCK' THEN 'A'
	 WHEN S.TYPE = 'LCV' THEN 'L'
     WHEN S.TYPE = 'TRAILER' THEN 'T'	 
	 WHEN S.TYPE = 'VL'  THEN 'V'
	 WHEN S.TYPE = 'SEMITRAILER' THEN 'S'
	 WHEN S.TYPE = 'NONE' THEN 'N'
	 ELSE 'N' END	<>	L.TYPE	OR
S.TCU_ID	<>	L.TCU_ID	OR
S.tcu_serial_number	<>	L.tcu_serial_number	OR
S.tcu_brand	<>	L.tcu_brand	OR
S.tcu_version	<>	L.tcu_version  OR
S.is_tcu_register	<>	L.is_tcu_register  OR
S.reference_date	<>	L.reference_date  OR
VP.ID     	<>	L.vehicle_property_id  OR
(SELECT EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM CAST(S.CREATED_AT AS TIMESTAMP)) * 1000)	<>	L.CREATED_AT  OR
S.model_id	<>	L.model_id  OR
CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(S.VIN,1,3) IS NOT NULL AND SUBSTRING(S.VIN,1,3) = TRIM(OM.VIN_PREFIX)
     THEN OM.ID
     ELSE (SELECT ID FROM MASTER.OEM WHERE TRIM(VIN_PREFIX) ISNULL)  END	<>	L.OEM_ID  OR
CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(S.VIN,1,3) IS NOT NULL AND SUBSTRING(S.VIN,1,3) = TRIM(OM.VIN_PREFIX)
     THEN OM.OEM_ORGANISATION_ID 
     ELSE (SELECT OEM_ORGANISATION_ID FROM MASTER.OEM WHERE TRIM(VIN_PREFIX) ISNULL)  END	<>	L.OEM_ORGANISATION_ID  OR
CASE WHEN S.STATUS = 'SUSPENDED' THEN 'U' ELSE 'H' END	<>	L.OPT_IN  OR
(SELECT EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM CAST(S.MODIFIED_AT AS TIMESTAMP)) * 1000)	<>	L.MODIFIED_AT  OR
S.IS_OTA	<>	L.IS_OTA  OR
S.MODIFIED_BY	<>	L.MODIFIED_BY  OR
S.FUEL_TYPE	<>	L.FUEL_TYPE  OR
  L.ID IS NULL
);

UPDATE MASTER.VEHICLE L 
SET	 
ORGANIZATION_ID	=	S.ORGANIZATION_ID	,
NAME	=	S.NAME	,
VIN	=	S.VIN	,
LICENSE_PLATE_NUMBER	=	S.LICENSE_PLATE_NUMBER	,
STATUS	=	S.STATUS	,
STATUS_CHANGED_DATE	=	S.STATUS_CHANGED_DATE	,
TERMINATION_DATE	=	S.TERMINATION_DATE	,
TYPE		=	S.TYPE	,
TCU_ID	=	S.TCU_ID	,
TCU_SERIAL_NUMBER	=	S.TCU_SERIAL_NUMBER	,
TCU_BRAND	=	S.TCU_BRAND	,
TCU_VERSION	=	S.TCU_VERSION	,
IS_TCU_REGISTER	=	S.IS_TCU_REGISTER  ,
REFERENCE_DATE	=	S.REFERENCE_DATE  ,
VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ID	=	S.VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ID  ,
CREATED_AT	=	S.CREATED_AT  ,
MODEL_ID	=	S.MODEL_ID  ,
OEM_ID	=	S.OEM_ID  ,
OEM_ORGANISATION_ID	=	S.OEM_ORGANISATION_ID  ,
OPT_IN	=	S.OPT_IN  ,
MODIFIED_AT	=	S.MODIFIED_AT  ,
IS_OTA	=	S.IS_OTA  ,
MODIFIED_BY	=	S.MODIFIED_BY  ,
FUEL_TYPE	=	S.FUEL_TYPE  
FROM    staging.Vehicle_CHG S
WHERE L.VID = S.VID 
AND L.VIN = S.VIN
  AND  S.CHG_FLG     = 'X';

select * from staging.vehicle_chg ;

SELECT 
E.ORGANIZATION_ID       ,
E.NAME                  ,
E.VIN                   ,
E.LICENSE_PLATE_NUMBER  ,
E.STATUS                ,
E.STATUS_CHANGED_DATE   ,
E.TERMINATION_DATE      ,
E.VID                   ,
E.TYPE                  ,
E.TCU_ID                ,
E.TCU_SERIAL_NUMBER     ,
E.TCU_BRAND             ,
E.TCU_VERSION           ,
E.IS_TCU_REGISTER       ,
E.REFERENCE_DATE        ,
E.VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ID   ,
E.CREATED_AT            ,
E.MODEL_ID              ,
E.OEM_ID                ,
E.OEM_ORGANISATION_ID   ,
E.OPT_IN                ,
E.MODIFIED_AT           ,
E.IS_OTA                ,
E.MODIFIED_BY           ,
E.FUEL_TYPE             
FROM staging.Vehicle_CHG E
WHERE  E.CHG_FLG = 'I' 
AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM MASTER.VEHICLE L
             WHERE   L.VIN = E.VIN) 
ORDER BY 
    	E.VIN;

SELECT distinct
vh.vehicle_vid,
Replace(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.frontAxleType'),'"','') as frontaxletype,
Replace(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.rearAxleLoad'),'"','') as rearaxleload,
Replace(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.rearAxleRatio'),'"','') as rearaxleratio,
Replace(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.tyreSizeRear1'),'"','') as TyreRearsize,
Replace(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.tyreSizeFrontAxle1'),'"','') as TyreFrontsize
from cle_pc_cvp_fap.vehicle vh
left join daf.co_connected_object co
on co.internal_id = vh.vehicle_vid
left join daf.co_connected_object_type typ
on typ.id = co.connected_object_type
left join daf.co_third_party prty
on typ.third_party_id = prty.id
where (Replace(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.frontAxleType'),'"','') is not null OR 
Replace(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.rearAxleLoad'),'"','') IS NOT NULL or
Replace(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.rearAxleRatio'),'"','') IS NOT NULL OR
Replace(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.tyreSizeRear1'),'"','')  IS NOT NULL OR
Replace(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.tyreSizeFrontAxle1'),'"','') IS NOT NULL);

do
$$
declare
    f record;
begin
    for f in SELECT vehicle_vid,frontaxletype,rearaxleload,rearaxleratio,TyreRearsize,TyreFrontsize
	from public.vehicleaxleproperties
    loop	    
	 INSERT INTO staging.Vehicleaxleproperties_chg
	 (
		 vehicle_id,
axle_type,
position,
type,
springs,
load,
ratio,
size,
chg_flg,
load_dt
)
SELECT distinct
      vh.id as vehicle_id,
			'F', 1, f.frontaxletype, null,null, null,f.TyreFrontsize,
CASE WHEN L.vehicle_id IS NULL THEN 'I' ELSE 'X' END AS CHG_FLG,
CURRENT_TIMeSTAMP AS LOAD_DT
FROM MASTER.VEHICLE vh
LEFT JOIN master.vehicleaxleproperties L
ON L.vehicle_id = vh.id 
WHERE vh.vid = f.vehicle_vid and ('1'  <> L.position  OR
	   f.frontaxletype  <> L.type OR
	   f.TyreFrontsize <> L.size OR
	   L.vehicle_ID is null)  AND L.axle_type = 'F';

	   end loop;
end;
$$;

select * from staging.vehicleaxleproperties_chg;

do
$$
declare
    f record;
begin
    for f in SELECT vehicle_vid,frontaxletype,rearaxleload,rearaxleratio,TyreRearsize,TyreFrontsize
	from public.vehicleaxleproperties
    loop	    
	 INSERT INTO staging.Vehicleaxleproperties_chg
	 (
		 vehicle_id,
axle_type,
position,
type,
springs,
load,
ratio,
size,
chg_flg,
load_dt
)
SELECT distinct
      vh.id as vehicle_id,
			'R',1, NULL,NULL, f.rearaxleload, f.rearaxleratio,f.TyreRearsize,
CASE WHEN L.vehicle_id IS NULL THEN 'I' ELSE 'X' END AS CHG_FLG,
CURRENT_TIMeSTAMP AS LOAD_DT
FROM MASTER.VEHICLE vh
LEFT JOIN master.vehicleaxleproperties L
ON L.vehicle_id = vh.id 
WHERE vh.vid = f.vehicle_vid and ('1'  <> L.position  OR
	   f.rearaxleload  <> L.load OR
	   f.rearaxleratio <> L.ratio OR
	   f.TyreRearsize <> L.size OR
	   L.vehicle_ID is null)  AND L.axle_type = 'R';

	   end loop;
end;
$$;

select * from staging.vehicleaxleproperties_chg;

select distinct vh.id,
vh.vehicle_vid,
vh.extra_chassis_number as chasis_fuel_tank_number,
vh.extra_volume_fuel_tank as chasis_fuel_tank_volume
from cle_pc_cvp_fap.vehicle vh
left join daf.co_connected_object co
on co.internal_id = vh.vehicle_vid
left join daf.co_connected_object_type typ
on typ.id = co.connected_object_type
left join daf.co_third_party prty
on typ.third_party_id = prty.id
WHERE vh.extra_chassis_number is not null;

activities.name: VehicleFuelTankProperties_CHG
activities.description: Compares source and target and find the records for upsert

source.query:
SELECT DISTINCT
	coalesce(L.ID,0) AS ID,
	vh.ID as VEHICLE_ID                      ,  
S.CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_NUMBER                              ,
S.CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_VOLUME                                       ,
	CASE WHEN L.ID IS NULL THEN 'I' ELSE 'X' END AS CHG_FLG,
	CURRENT_TIMeSTAMP AS LOAD_DT
	
FROM
       public.VehicleFuelTankProperties S
JOIN master.vehicle vh
on vh.vid = S.vehicle_vid
LEFT JOIN 
       master.VehicleFuelTankProperties L
ON vh.id = L.vehicle_id

WHERE (
S.CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_NUMBER	<>	L.CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_NUMBER  OR
	S.CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_VOLUME	<>	L.CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_VOLUME  OR
	    L.ID IS NULL
);

UPDATE MASTER.VehicleFuelTankProperties L 
SET	 
CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_NUMBER	=	S.CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_NUMBER  ,
CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_VOLUME	=	S.CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_VOLUME  
FROM    staging.VehicleFuelTankProperties_CHG S
WHERE L.vehicle_id = S.vehicle_id 
  AND  S.CHG_FLG     = 'X';

select * from staging.vehiclefueltankproperties_chg;

SELECT 
E.vehicle_id       ,
E.CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_NUMBER                  ,
E.CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_VOLUME
FROM staging.VehicleFuelTankProperties_CHG E
WHERE  E.CHG_FLG = 'I' 
AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM MASTER.VehicleFuelTankProperties L
             WHERE    L.vehicle_id = E.vehicle_id)
ORDER BY 
    	CHASIS_FUEL_TANK_NUMBER;

SELECT distinct
vh.vehicle_creation_date as manufacture_date,
null as delivery_date,
vh.brand as make,
vh.extra_length as length,
vh.extra_height as height,
vh.extra_gross_weight as weight,
null as engine_id,
vh.extra_engine_type as engine_type,
vh.engine_power,
vh.extra_coolant as engine_coolant,
CASE WHEN vh.emission_level  is NULL THEN vh.CO2_NORM END as engine_emission_level,
vh.extra_chassis_number as chasis_id,
vh.extra_rear_overhang as chasis_rear_overhang,
case when vh.axle_configuration is null then REPLACE(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.wheelPlanType'),'"','') end  as driveline_axle_configuration,
vh.extra_wheel_base as driveline_wheel_base,
vh.extra_tyre_size_front_axle_1 as driveline_tire_size,
null as transmission_gearbox_id,
vh.extra_gearbox_type  as transmission_gearbox_type,
vh.extra_chassis_number as cabin_id,
null as series_id,
REPLACE(JSON_EXTRACT(co.metadata,'$.sdType'),'"','') as  series_vehicle_range,
case when vh.model_year is null then vh.construction_year end as model_year,
vh.extra_cab_type as cabin_type,
vh.extra_roof_spoiler  as cabin_roofspoiler,
'ECU Type' as electronic_control_unit_type,
'ECU control unit (SCU)' as electronic_control_unit_name,
'Gross' as weight_type,
CASE WHEN vh.extra_side_skirts = 'side skirts' THEN 'Yes' ELSE 'No' END AS chasis_side_skirts,
CASE WHEN vh.extra_side_collars = 'side collars' THEN 'Yes' ELSE 'No' END AS chasis_side_collar,
vh.extra_width  as width,
vh.model_name as type_id,
vh.vehicle_vid

from cle_pc_cvp_fap.vehicle vh
left join daf.co_connected_object co
on co.internal_id = vh.vehicle_vid
left join daf.co_connected_object_type typ
on typ.id = co.connected_object_type
left join daf.co_third_party prty
on typ.third_party_id = prty.id
left join cle_pc_cvp_fap.equipment eq
on eq.vehicle_id = vh.id
where vh.extra_chassis_number is not null;

activities.name: VehicleProperties_CHG
activities.description: Compares source and target and find the records for upsert

source.query:
SELECT DISTINCT
	coalesce(L.ID,0) AS ID,
	(select extract(epoch from cast(vp_dup.MANUFACTURE_DATE as timestamp))  * 1000) as MANUFACTURE_DATE,
  
S.DELIVERY_DATE                              ,
S.MAKE                                       ,
S.LENGTH                                     ,
S.HEIGHT                                     ,
S.WEIGHT                                     ,
S.ENGINE_ID                                  ,
S.ENGINE_TYPE                                ,
S.ENGINE_POWER                               ,
S.ENGINE_COOLANT                             ,
S.ENGINE_EMISSION_LEVEL                      ,
S.CHASIS_ID                                  ,
S.CHASIS_REAR_OVERHANG                       ,
S.DRIVELINE_AXLE_CONFIGURATION               ,
S.DRIVELINE_WHEEL_BASE                       ,
S.DRIVELINE_TIRE_SIZE                        ,
S.TRANSMISSION_GEARBOX_ID                    ,
S.TRANSMISSION_GEARBOX_TYPE                  ,

select distinct prty.external_id as org_id,co.internal_id as vid,pk.external_id as packagecode,
/*cos.commercial_service_name,*/
sub.activation_date,sub.end_date,sub.status
from daf.co_third_party prty
join daf.co_pack_subscription pkg
on pkg.third_party_id = prty.id
join daf.co_resource_subscription sub
on sub.pack_subscription_id = pkg.id
join daf.co_commercial_subscription cs
on cs.resource_subscription_id = sub.id
join daf.co_link_pack_commercial_service pcs
on pcs.pack_id = pkg.pack_id
join daf.co_commercial_service cos
on cos.id = pcs.commercial_service_id
join daf.co_connected_object co
on co.id = sub.resource_id
join daf.co_pack pk
on pk.id = pkg.pack_id
where  prty.external_id in (select distinct customer_id from daf_ct_wl.priority_customers);

activities.name: Group_Chg_Accounts
activities.description: Makes default dynamic group for Accounts

source.query:
SELECT DISTINCT
'A' as object_type,
'D' as group_type,
'A' as function_enum            ,
S.id as organization_id,
'All accounts' as name                     ,
'All accounts' as description              ,
(select extract(epoch from now()) * 1000) as created_at,
CASE WHEN L.organization_id IS NULL THEN 'I' ELSE 'X' END AS CHG_FLG,
CURRENT_TIMeSTAMP AS LOAD_DT
from master.organization S
left join master.group L
ON S.ID = L.organization_id
where ('D' <> L.group_type OR
  'A'  <> L.function_enum OR
  'All accounts'  <> L.name  OR
  'All accounts' <> L.description OR
  L.organization_id IS NULL)
  
  UNION

SELECT DISTINCT
'V' as object_type,
'D' as group_type,
'A' as function_enum            ,
S.id as organization_id,
'Fleet' as name                     ,
'Fleet' as description              ,
(select extract(epoch from now()) * 1000) as created_at,
CASE WHEN L.organization_id IS NULL THEN 'I' ELSE 'X' END AS CHG_FLG,
CURRENT_TIMeSTAMP AS LOAD_DT
from master.organization S
left join master.group L
ON S.ID = L.organization_id
where ('D' <> L.group_type OR
  'A'  <> L.function_enum OR
  'Fleet'  <> L.name  OR
  'Fleet' <> L.description OR
  L.organization_id IS NULL);

SELECT 
E.object_type       ,
E.group_type                  ,
E.function_enum,
E.organization_id,
E.name,
E.description,
E.created_at
FROM staging.Group_CHG E
WHERE  E.CHG_FLG = 'I' 
AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM MASTER.GROUP L
             WHERE    L.organization_id = E.organization_id)
ORDER BY 
    	E.organization_id;

UPDATE MASTER.GROUP L 
SET	 
object_type	=	S.object_type  ,
group_type	=	S.group_type,  
function_enum	=	S.function_enum  ,
name	=	S.name  ,
description	=	S.description  
FROM    staging.GROUP_CHG S
WHERE L.organization_id = S.organization_id 
  AND  S.CHG_FLG     = 'X';

SELECT * FROM STAGING.GROUP_CHG;
